  "description": "<p><strong><span style=\"line-height: 0px;\">﻿</span>微软上周在美国旧金山召开的开发者大会（Build）宣布，开放Windows 8.1系统预览版下载，并预计正式版将在年底上市。市场调查机构Gartner指出，Windows 8.1的新功能有望终结外界对微软的批评。</strong>在最新的Windows 8.1系统中，微软重点提升了个性化体验，强化了Bing搜索功能，增加了商业应用功能，并预装了一些全新的App（应用程序）等。最新预装的App包括Facebook、Flipboard和NFL等。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1e8564/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243232.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%B0%86%E5%8A%A9%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E6%89%B9%E8%AF%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243232.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%B0%86%E5%8A%A9%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E6%89%B9%E8%AF%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243232.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%B0%86%E5%8A%A9%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E6%89%B9%E8%AF%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243232.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%B0%86%E5%8A%A9%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E6%89%B9%E8%AF%84\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243232.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9AWindows+8.1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%